Communicating With Your Manager

2.1 Communicating With Your Manager (5min)

What's is their official job?

1.Flex and modify, based on the situation
2.Pro-actively communicate
3.State what you need upfront

Non-verbal communication

"How am I going to tell my manager THIS?"

